  <h2>A Fresh Take on Tailoring</h2>
  <p>The marriage of traditional tailoring with a fashion-forward eye is the cornerstone of our design aesthetic.</p>
  <p>By taking a few cues from menswear and focusing on style, we have transformed professional wear into wardrobe essentials. We achieve that by paying special attention to the details and getting the fit truly right. Quincy garments are defined by figure-flattering silhouettes and seaming, intricate trims, silky linings; and perfectly placed buttons, darts and vents.</p>
  <img class="fit" src="{{ 'fit-image.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Chelsea Blazer">
